{"tid":333797,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"職安真漢子彈琴獻技 浪漫滿商場","createTime":"2017-07-24T07:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T10:59:04.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e92088ba04df5824d0774d41f908dc455739ece","tid":333797,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/YjmxrcUbcjHi3OFvxMYUng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/afcadb00f800bdd50d1f44d09755eaf5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYjmxrcUbcjHi3OFvxMYUng--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fafcadb00f800bdd50d1f44d09755eaf5&h=734104a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每天出入沙塵滾滾的工地、汗流浹背地運送大大小小的建築物料，地盤內的「職安真漢子」一向予人粗獷、威猛的形象，不過，原來他們都有柔情浪漫一面。近日就有一名地盤工人，乘着午間空檔走入商場，不過他並非只是「涼冷氣」，反而在鋼琴上大顯身手，網民看後都不禁大呼：「邊個話地盤佬無文化？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短片開始時，只見一名身穿黃色反光衣的男子背向鏡頭，叮叮咚咚地敲打琴鍵。雖然環境甚為嘈雜，旁邊又有一名白衣小孩不停鬧着玩，不過彈琴男子都未有分心，專心一致地陶醉在自己的音樂世界。看過影片的網友認為，該名男子應是一個「浪漫的地盤佬」，紛紛對他的藝術氣息讚口不絕。亦有網民指出，「好多師傅都係臥虎藏龍」，認為地盤工人不應被社會看輕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8abbc727965c40a47911cec734b1e61041048d4","tid":333797,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"263ddb1781b43c508071ba835943240ec0e7f3c5","tid":333797,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"片呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d051d4edf2d13c6a3b138694373ed86d82bd136c","tid":333797,"uid":331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:35:15.0